Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.02,0:00:09.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陛下
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.20,0:00:11.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遗体已经送达了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.55,0:00:15.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在我正和克洛维斯说话
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.34,0:00:18.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要抓紧时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.53,0:00:20.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最终的觉悟
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.31,0:01:54.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fad(600,0)\pos(424,395)}STAGE 6
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.71,0:01:54.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fad(600,0)\pos(424,430)}被夺走的假面
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.44,0:02:00.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嫌疑犯吧  克洛维斯殿下那件事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.01,0:02:02.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师说是抓错人了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.67,0:02:04.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但肯定是哪里比较可疑才会被抓的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.04,0:02:07.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该不会是恐怖分子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.99,0:02:10.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是当然的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.66,0:02:12.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学校至少会做确认的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.03,0:02:14.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然是11区住民
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.44,0:02:16.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是名誉布里塔尼亚人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.22,0:02:18.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但这不是一回事嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.15,0:02:19.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能老是害怕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.06,0:02:22.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不和他说话怎么能知道他是怎么样的人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.26,0:02:25.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的行动力高过头了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.01,0:02:56.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,七年不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.81,0:02:57.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个暗号
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.14,0:02:59.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去屋顶天台说话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.10,0:03:00.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.18,0:03:03.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我放心了  你没事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.16,0:03:05.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多亏了你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.74,0:03:08.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你才是 如果你不保护我的话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.42,0:03:11.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是把欠你的还给你而已
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.22,0:03:12.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,七年前的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.71,0:03:16.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个女孩呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.64,0:03:17.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是那个在密封舱里的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.21,0:03:20.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在战斗的混乱中失散了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.27,0:03:23.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那里知道些什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.37,0:03:23.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.34,0:03:27.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎除了亲卫队以外谁也不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.50,0:03:29.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.08,0:03:32.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名字  还是叫你鲁路修吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.89,0:03:35.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前的我在资料里已经死了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.80,0:03:38.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鲁路修·兰佩洛奇
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.31,0:03:39.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在这样称呼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.27,0:03:40.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.77,0:03:42.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那边才是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.73,0:03:44.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,军事法庭怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.76,0:03:46.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且居然能转入这里
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.73,0:03:48.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也吓了一跳啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.29,0:03:50.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到鲁路修居然在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.23,0:03:51.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.09,0:03:53.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了让搜查工作能够确实进行
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.01,0:03:55.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有个人助了我一臂之力
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.00,0:03:56.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个人还说
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.98,0:03:59.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,17岁的话就应该去学校
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.05,0:04:09.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些全都是克洛维斯哥哥的画吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.28,0:04:09.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.79,0:04:14.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,温柔的色彩
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.85,0:04:16.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是哥哥吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.58,0:04:21.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逼近敌方基地成功
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.84,0:04:22.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.72,0:04:24.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,推测根据地的位置
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.35,0:04:26.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,统筹好情报
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.21,0:04:27.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes My Lord
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.31,0:04:40.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会吧  科奈莉娅?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.76,0:04:44.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,旧时代的遗物
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.37,0:05:00.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,达尔顿  是在这里面吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.37,0:05:01.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs20\fsp-1}{\fad(100,100)\a6)}[安德列·达尔顿 Andres Darlton]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.02,0:05:02.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  您打算怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.97,0:05:03.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们也
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.73,0:05:05.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种战力差的不需要你们支援
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.44,0:05:05.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.65,0:05:11.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,投降吧  愚蠢的11区人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.40,0:05:12.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布里塔尼亚的混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.57,0:05:17.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ZERO好像不在嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.80,0:05:20.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样一个个歼灭真是没完没了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.55,0:05:23.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们就在这里腐烂吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.00,0:05:28.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了  哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.03,0:05:31.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎回来  娜娜莉  {\fnDFPHSGothic-W5\fe128\fs26\b1\alpha&H15&}咲{\r}世子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.25,0:05:34.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天我有礼物要给你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.48,0:05:36.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.81,0:06:08.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这手
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.33,0:06:11.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.85,0:06:14.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你果然  没事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.76,0:06:17.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久不见  娜娜莉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.43,0:06:22.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朱雀  今天能留下来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.39,0:06:24.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朱雀已经是这个学校的学生了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.84,0:06:26.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以无论什么时候都能见面
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.05,0:06:27.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.18,0:06:29.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为有军队的工作在
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.05,0:06:31.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能每天都见面就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.92,0:06:32.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,军队
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.33,0:06:34.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还要继续吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.85,0:06:35.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.89,0:06:38.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我被分配到技术部了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.33,0:06:39.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会那么危险哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.00,0:06:40.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.97,0:06:42.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,技术部吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.72,0:06:45.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.73,0:06:47.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好好坐着
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.33,0:06:50.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和七年前不同  今天我是主人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.15,0:06:55.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好像变得稳重了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.30,0:06:57.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你变得豪爽了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.46,0:06:58.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.37,0:07:02.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是让你在房间待着嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.18,0:07:04.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个男人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.61,0:07:07.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我们在新宿遇到的那个布里塔尼亚军人嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.36,0:07:08.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.53,0:07:09.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.27,0:07:11.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.78,0:07:15.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是  我的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.96,0:07:18.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出来  杰雷米亚
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.74,0:07:19.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉尔弗德卿
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.74,0:07:21.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs20\fsp-1}{\fad(100,100)\a6)}[吉尔伯特·G.P.·吉尔弗德 Gilbert G.P. Guilford]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.02,0:07:21.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你终于能理解了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.86,0:07:23.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是关于谋反方面的谈话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.30,0:07:25.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ORANGE
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.20,0:07:31.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且  你们纯血派放走了ZERO的事实不会改变
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.48,0:07:33.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的官阶被降了三级
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.39,0:07:36.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的选择有两个
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.55,0:07:38.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从一个普通机师开始从头来过
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.89,0:07:41.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或是继续耕耘你的橘子田
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.97,0:07:43.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再来玩哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.22,0:07:45.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,娜娜莉也会高兴的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.65,0:07:47.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  但是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.57,0:07:49.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鲁路修
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.57,0:07:51.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们在学校还是装作不认识吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.98,0:07:52.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.93,0:07:54.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要怎么解释
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.86,0:07:57.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和名誉布里塔尼亚人是朋友什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.53,0:07:59.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弄不好还会暴露
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.60,0:08:01.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是皇子这件事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.53,0:08:04.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,娜娜莉也是一样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.40,0:08:06.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想再给你们添更多的麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.81,0:08:09.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上次你也是  老是顾及其他人的…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.78,0:08:09.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上次?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.35,0:08:11.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.66,0:08:13.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.98,0:08:15.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.36,0:08:16.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见  明天见
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.68,0:08:20.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总觉得  很高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.46,0:08:25.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没想到会有说这些话的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.43,0:08:35.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你昨天好像有点奇怪哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.63,0:08:37.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不在学生会露下脸
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.89,0:08:39.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界史考得不太好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.17,0:08:41.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别谦虚了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.36,0:08:42.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你从来没有…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.48,0:08:54.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然新闻还没有播
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.78,0:08:57.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,科奈莉娅把武士的基地给毁了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.80,0:08:59.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们可是中部最大的组织
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.80,0:09:00.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一瞬就被
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.06,0:09:03.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ZERO  我们再这样下去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.97,0:09:04.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要着急
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.08,0:09:06.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要等待时机
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.39,0:09:06.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.24,0:09:08.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次我会联系你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.10,0:09:12.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是个缠人的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.94,0:09:14.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经到极限了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.71,0:09:22.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs20\fsp-1}{\fad(100,100)\a6)}[滚回…贫民区]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.01,0:09:30.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮娜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.61,0:09:33.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  我吵到你了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.28,0:09:35.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  那没有关系
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.40,0:09:36.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么没去学校
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.59,0:09:38.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生什么事了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.72,0:09:41.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  有点…害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.31,0:09:43.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,害怕?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.30,0:09:45.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们班里来了个转校生
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.75,0:09:48.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀害克洛维斯殿下的嫌疑犯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.03,0:09:50.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是11区人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.97,0:10:00.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总是承蒙关照
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.76,0:10:04.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接收姓名是男性的没关系吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.92,0:10:15.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藏假面的地方吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.49,0:10:16.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和Geass不同
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.82,0:10:19.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这东西可是能成为确实证据的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.84,0:10:24.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥  我泡了茶
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.01,0:10:27.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊呀  这个味道  又是批萨?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.20,0:10:29.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在攒积分
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.30,0:10:31.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我马上就下来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.09,0:10:32.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.14,0:10:36.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近有没有变得软绵绵的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.14,0:10:36.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs20\fsp-1}{\fad(100,100)\a6)}[意指吃必胜客吃到虚胖哦~虚胖~]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.88,0:10:37.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如说上臂之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.76,0:10:40.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对不准碰哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.46,0:10:41.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇  好可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.71,0:10:58.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.08,0:11:00.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就在想会不会发生这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.08,0:11:02.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让朱雀辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.03,0:11:04.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  那个
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.54,0:11:08.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种事需要花时间
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.41,0:11:10.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能想想办法吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.23,0:11:12.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们是朋友啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.14,0:11:24.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说 还给我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.24,0:11:26.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.84,0:11:34.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么能让猫
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.69,0:11:35.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不就是只猫嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.43,0:11:37.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别开玩笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.95,0:11:40.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么能因为这么白痴的事而暴露
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.23,0:11:44.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.22,0:11:47.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可没有碰哦  嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.33,0:11:55.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  没错
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.80,0:11:59.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像被猫抢走了很重要的东西似的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.22,0:12:00.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重要的东西是指
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.59,0:12:02.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我不是很清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.44,0:12:05.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但肯定是很重要的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.54,0:12:08.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为哥哥那种惨叫声
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.74,0:12:10.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还是第一次听到
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.90,0:12:13.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鲁路修重要的东西究竟是什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.92,0:12:14.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情书?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.13,0:12:16.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尴尬的相片
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.46,0:12:17.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,写诗的小册子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.17,0:12:18.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.09,0:12:21.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,包在我们身上
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.33,0:12:24.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对会比鲁路修先一步抢回来给你看看
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.63,0:12:25.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要抢先
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.81,0:12:30.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果这时候那些恐怖分子在的话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.47,0:12:31.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就能展开包围作战了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.35,0:12:32.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡莲
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.29,0:12:34.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  不行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.35,0:12:35.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能再被她怀疑了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.97,0:12:45.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然出这种丑
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.02,0:12:48.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我就去了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.06,0:12:50.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯嗯  然后呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.33,0:12:51.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后那个人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.80,0:12:53.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这只猫怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.26,0:12:55.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是那个假面吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.94,0:12:56.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个ZERO的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.06,0:12:58.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会吧  为什么会在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.28,0:13:00.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.63,0:13:03.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我忘掉  刚才看到的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.45,0:13:08.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.93,0:13:09.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.18,0:13:13.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是学生会长米蕾·阿修佛德
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.33,0:13:14.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猫!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.09,0:13:16.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猫?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.17,0:13:19.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在立即去抓在校内逃窜的猫咪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.97,0:13:21.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,课外活动全部暂停
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.73,0:13:24.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,协助我们的社团可以享受经费优待
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.40,0:13:28.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且  抓住猫的人还有超豪华奖品
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.66,0:13:31.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以获得学生会成员的吻
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.14,0:13:38.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学生会也就是说  我的?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.26,0:13:39.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.39,0:13:41.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在学生会进出的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.92,0:13:43.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大小姐的嘴唇
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.61,0:13:45.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该不是亲在脸颊这种地方吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.00,0:13:47.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  现在就算脸颊也无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.06,0:13:49.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  可以指定位置吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.89,0:13:53.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.38,0:13:57.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.30,0:13:58.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的第一次
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.17,0:14:00.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学生会会员的话就是说
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.76,0:14:02.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鲁路修也可以?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.82,0:14:04.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想要米蕾的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.98,0:14:06.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就不要做白日梦了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.18,0:14:10.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,机动力的话是我们占优势
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.19,0:14:13.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快找木天蓼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.19,0:14:14.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs20\fsp-1}{\fad(100,100)\a6)}[木天蓼：猫最喜欢的草本兴奋剂]
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.62,0:14:14.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,越硬越好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.83,0:14:15.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猫
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.80,0:14:16.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抓到猫以后
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.49,0:14:17.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有物就交给我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.89,0:14:18.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交给我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.52,0:14:19.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交给我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.08,0:14:22.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会长  多管闲事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.22,0:14:25.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,随便把人当成奖品处理
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.71,0:14:27.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我才对布里塔尼亚的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.29,0:14:27.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.15,0:14:30.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的真的  很厉害吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.00,0:14:32.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很厉害  认真的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.06,0:14:34.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.59,0:14:36.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不设定成病弱小姐就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.91,0:14:40.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.78,0:14:43.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那是什么打扮啊  莎莉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.31,0:14:47.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可关系到我们的吻啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.61,0:14:49.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同感
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.67,0:14:53.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,娜娜莉  那只猫有没有什么特征吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.43,0:14:54.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.95,0:14:56.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得它的脚不太好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.63,0:14:58.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脚步声稍微有点奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.21,0:14:59.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.55,0:15:03.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那只猫是这么叫的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.68,0:15:06.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喵~
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.52,0:15:10.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是悠闲的学校
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.63,0:15:12.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在还是服丧期啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.50,0:15:15.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朱雀没问题吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.23,0:15:17.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起那个  这里的大学
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.21,0:15:19.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这件事已经和他们谈妥了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.20,0:15:20.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.10,0:15:24.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是也不用把Lancelot赶出去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.56,0:15:25.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.19,0:15:28.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还说编号住民不行
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.68,0:15:29.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让你久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.33,0:15:33.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了  我们学生会的人抓住它的话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.97,0:15:35.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也有奖品吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.38,0:15:37.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吻的事?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.71,0:15:38.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.97,0:15:39.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.63,0:15:42.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶尔也要拿出来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.76,0:15:43.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干劲这种东西
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.70,0:15:49.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说  不准在校内飙车
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.32,0:15:55.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样我们的吻就保住了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.48,0:15:57.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,后方就拜托莎莉了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.81,0:16:00.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.38,0:16:02.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.07,0:16:04.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吻的权利
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.30,0:16:05.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想对谁用
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.81,0:16:07.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道是  鲁鲁?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.24,0:16:10.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为…为什么会想成那样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.61,0:16:13.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为…那个嘛…这个
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.81,0:16:18.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.62,0:16:23.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朱雀
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.62,0:16:24.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鲁路修
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.44,0:16:25.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也来追猫咪?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.08,0:16:29.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在上面吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.11,0:16:30.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下  朱雀
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.60,0:16:33.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你赶快回去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.71,0:16:35.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  学生会长说要抓住它
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.09,0:16:36.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了啦  你快回去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.16,0:16:37.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猫就由我来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.01,0:16:39.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是我比较擅长运动
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.31,0:16:41.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上次小鸟逃掉的时候也是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.03,0:16:43.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要把那么久的事拿出来提
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.78,0:16:45.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只不过七年前而已
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.26,0:16:46.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.10,0:16:50.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是一如既往的体力笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.01,0:16:54.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经追到了是真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.57,0:16:55.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁发现了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.01,0:16:56.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那里
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.81,0:17:00.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朱雀
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.96,0:17:02.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系  不要怕
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.06,0:17:04.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朱雀 不要
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.36,0:17:05.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系  交给我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.51,0:17:09.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.68,0:17:11.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前明明更加个人主义的才对
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.91,0:17:16.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鲁路修
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.08,0:17:24.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧  鲁路修
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.05,0:17:26.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.79,0:17:28.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那两个人  难道
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.58,0:17:45.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也太放心了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.10,0:17:48.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像力气都提不起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.11,0:17:51.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.50,0:17:52.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鲁路修的危机
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.95,0:17:54.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被转校生救了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.74,0:17:59.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是上次那只猫嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.33,0:18:14.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你  救了鲁鲁
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.60,0:18:16.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真行啊  转校生
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.65,0:18:18.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这只猫是不是拿着什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.94,0:18:20.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像戴着什么似的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.84,0:18:22.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我没有看清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.93,0:18:24.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道什么时候掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.12,0:18:25.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鲁鲁呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.37,0:18:29.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说有东西忘了  让我先出来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.87,0:18:30.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是那个
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.86,0:18:32.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙的『尴尬的秘密』
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.10,0:18:34.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来是这样  会长
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.87,0:18:41.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难得有机会可以抓住你的弱点
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.71,0:18:43.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鲁鲁太会装帅了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.74,0:18:50.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  你们两个人认识吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.07,0:18:52.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为  和11区住民…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.62,0:18:57.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.23,0:18:59.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.11,0:19:00.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会长
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.30,0:19:03.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能不能让他进学生会
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.21,0:19:05.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的学校规定
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.42,0:19:07.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要进某一个社团
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.68,0:19:09.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.18,0:19:14.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,副会长的拜托
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.14,0:19:16.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是没有办法
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.07,0:19:20.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这件事终于可以放心了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.45,0:19:22.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两位  耳朵凑过来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.30,0:19:31.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,娜娜莉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.84,0:19:34.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米蕾说的奖励
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.39,0:19:35.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为是两个人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.91,0:19:37.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以只能由还是准会员的我来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.86,0:19:39.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勉强完成了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.72,0:19:42.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  为了庆祝抓住猫咪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.55,0:19:44.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然是新人请客
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.79,0:19:45.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要擅自决定
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.28,0:19:48.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是莎莉  多多关照
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.56,0:19:49.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是利瓦尔
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.02,0:19:52.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是学生会长米蕾·阿修佛德
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.74,0:19:56.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请多多关照
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.92,0:20:21.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神圣布里塔尼亚帝国
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.92,0:20:26.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第98代  裘易斯陛下发言
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.13,0:20:34.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人  不是平等的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.10,0:20:38.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出生以来就有脚程快之人  美貌之人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.07,0:20:43.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父母贫困之人  拥有病弱躯体之人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.96,0:20:49.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出生  成长  才能  人类全都  各不相同
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.64,0:20:51.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.71,0:20:54.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人就是为了被差别对待而存在的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.01,0:20:57.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以人类才会争斗  竞争
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.83,0:21:00.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这之中便产生了信徒
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.77,0:21:03.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不平等并不是邪恶
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.02,0:21:05.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平等才是邪恶
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.53,0:21:09.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把权利平等起来的EU是怎样的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.53,0:21:09.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs20\fsp-1}{\fad(100,100)\a6)}[EU：Europe Union，假想的欧洲同盟]
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.62,0:21:12.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,任期这种东西只会导致愚昧的政治
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.62,0:21:12.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs20\fsp-1}{\fad(100,100)\a6)}[任期：同帝国继承制相反]
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.15,0:21:17.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,追求平等均富的中华联邦里都是懈怠的人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.59,0:21:21.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我们布里塔尼亚不同
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.04,0:21:25.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,争斗  竞争中总会伴随着进化
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.21,0:21:28.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进化  真是一个好词
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.20,0:21:31.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有布里塔尼亚在前进
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.52,0:21:33.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向着未来在前进
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.41,0:21:37.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吾子克洛维斯的死
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.45,0:21:41.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是布里塔尼亚在继续进化的证明
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.93,0:21:43.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战斗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.87,0:21:46.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,争斗  抢夺  获得  支配
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.43,0:21:50.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那尽头  有未来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.70,0:21:53.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布里塔尼亚万岁
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.65,0:22:09.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布里塔尼亚万岁…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.75,0:22:12.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鲁路修的敌人…吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.88,0:23:50.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亲情这个词是那么淡薄
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.27,0:23:51.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.16,0:23:55.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果那个男人是布里塔尼亚的象征的话就只有摧毁他
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.43,0:23:56.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使在这条路上还有皇姐
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.16,0:23:58.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,科奈莉娅也不会改变
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.35,0:24:01.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们还不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.40,0:24:02.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我拥有力量
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.49,0:24:04.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要有Geass
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.96,0:24:06.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一个人也
